{"tid":2260913,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"減緩 OLED 螢幕「PWM調光」傷眼問題！","createTime":"2020-10-28T02:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T11:47:51.000Z","uid":109923,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8327af9a422ea06f5516d3043b3f66dbc86aa7d6","tid":2260913,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T02:49:53.000Z","msg":"眾所周知，OLED 螢幕「PWM調光」喺低亮度嘅情況下，閃爍頻率降低會傷眼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMrv11y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMrv11y.jpg&h=f6bfd78b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\niPhone XR（LCD 螢幕）閃爍頻率超過 9,000Hz；<br />\n iPhone 11 Pro: 290.7 Hz @ &lt; 100% brightness<br />\niPhone Xs: 240.4 Hz @ &lt; 100% brightness<br />\niPhone X: 240.4 Hz @ &lt; 100% brightness<br />\n<br />\n如果你係用iPhone可以開啟「降低白點值」，An機求其喺Google play下載PWM保護/OLED saver之類嘅App都做到<br />\n<br />\n螢幕睇起嚟更暗，所以亮度可以校返高，亮度高咗「螢幕閃爍頻率」就會變高，可以舒緩視覺疲勞，同時亦都會更慳電 &amp; 減緩OLED烙印問題<br />\n<br />\n左邊低亮度 vs 右邊高亮度+降低白點值90%<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X01v11x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX01v11x.jpg&h=1e40d935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n注意！「PWM調光嘅低亮度」並非真正調整亮度，只係校緊個閃爍頻率，OLED螢幕實際上仲係保持「最高亮度」，只係人眼因閃爍頻率降低而認定螢幕變暗咗，如果開啟「降低白點值」就係將OLED「最高亮度」都降低埋<br />\n<br />\nLCD螢幕除非喺夜晚熄燈+校到最低亮度都唔夠暗，咁先至好開「降低白點值」，平時記得熄返「降低白點值」，因為LCD螢幕開「降低白點值+高亮度」會食更多電！<br />\n<br />\n減少白點值用喺LCD螢幕上就只係降低對比度，令偏光片擋更多背光，LED背光燈本身嘅亮度係不變，即係相同亮度之下發光效率降低，而且殘影更嚴重，因為LCD「最暗轉最光」同「最光轉最暗」嘅響應時間最短，gray to gray灰階響應時間最長<br />\n<br />\nLCD vs OLED 120hz殘影<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/u8aLHTM.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu8aLHTM.gif&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=89a7333e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/u8aLHTM.gif</a><br />\n90hz嘅OLED效果足以媲美120hz LCD"},{"pid":"258575c899d786d8ec39ea9cb6dc2d326c475cbe","tid":2260913,"uid":27324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:05:44.000Z","msg":"用緊XS 所以我應該降低白點值90%再加高亮度?"},{"pid":"5be2fea5941ff6e17b8a27da7ec75ef3a00c5a8a","tid":2260913,"uid":143305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:10:22.000Z","msg":"較dark mode會點"},{"pid":"2b5fd68b5b89695cea38be4256cbabe87621176c","tid":2260913,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:48:22.000Z","msg":"Reduce white point+ Zoom降低亮度+brightness100% 應該係最work"},{"pid":"5c678c43b650a92f03ebb8a858d2bc712f57e1fe","tid":2260913,"uid":51114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:05:04.000Z","msg":"iphone12係咪冇呢個問題？"},{"pid":"0d22c6a57bb1c136f7ea957c0960b41b8731cc15","tid":2260913,"uid":143412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:19:51.000Z","msg":"較dark mode, edge 仲係有pixel flickering<br />\n係咪OLED一定係咁？"},{"pid":"88463f1a3942ea4b03b92409fad60fb037619fe6","tid":2260913,"uid":66833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3492cd57a9e06d7efb9a67c37a3be91f35133ca1","tid":2260913,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:47:51.000Z","msg":"oled 真係睇到眼痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}